-- Itaú shares jump after bank posts record profit in second quarter
-- By Guillermo Parra-Bernal
-- Tue Aug 05, 2014 09:13AM EDT
-- None



SAO PAULO, Aug 5 (Reuters) - Preferred shares of Itaú Unibanco Holding SA <ITUB4.SA> surged 3 percent on Tuesday after Brazil's largest bank by market value posted record second-quarter profit and beat analysts' estimates.

